// VideoDemo.astro -- Video placeholder with command map link
---

<section class="py-24 hero-gradient" data-reveal>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-text mb-8">
      See it in action
    </h2>

    <div class="max-w-[960px] mx-auto aspect-video rounded-2xl border border-border bg-surface flex items-center justify-center">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 items-center">
        <span class="text-text-dim font-mono text-lg">Demo video coming soon</span>
        <a href="/command-map" class="text-accent hover:text-accent/80 text-sm">
          Explore the command map instead
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
